{"tid":2356385,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家開始聽到刷鞋仔同你講股票未？","createTime":"2021-01-06T19:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T21:57:38.000Z","uid":63048,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4773855648b4e3a4a4db9064df47bc0b231c390b","tid":2356385,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://journal.eyeprophet.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournal.eyeprophet.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2F20130524.jpg&h=833bda30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_cvdgPlEKW9k/TJ1jo85jTKI/AAAAAAAABcU/ckjY4Zl6GXQ/s1600/Bubble_Phases.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F_cvdgPlEKW9k%2FTJ1jo85jTKI%2FAAAAAAAABcU%2FckjY4Zl6GXQ%2Fs1600%2FBubble_Phases.jpg&h=e6ed0ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擦鞋童理論（shoeshine boy theory），又稱零股理論（Odd Lot Theory）是1927年由甘迺迪政治家族的約瑟夫&middot;派屈克&middot;甘迺迪（Joseph P. Kennedy, Sr.）所提出，是一種股市理論，意指當擦鞋童都在討論股票投資的時候，就是股市交易達到最高峰之時，之後就會下跌。<br />\n<br />\n擦鞋童是社會上較底層的經濟弱勢者，這些人通常沒有多餘的資金，可以進行股票投資，所以他們不太會關心股票的漲跌，或是談論股票的話題。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n如果有那麼一天，股價持續上漲，買股票就能賺錢，炒股成為全民運動，連一向不談股票的擦鞋童也忍不住將僅有的一點錢拿去投資股票，並且能跟客人侃侃而談，滿口股票經，甚至還能向客人報「明牌」時，那可能就是股價的最高點了，因為連最後資金最少的人，都已投入股巿，表示最後一隻老鼠已經出現，巿場已無新的資金新的買盤來支撐，股價可能很快就要大跌了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係香港大家可能少幫襯刷鞋，但係當賣菜阿姐、洗頭仔、樓下看更都同你講股票果陣，應該都到哂頂。同埋呢排見太多連登股神，一年回報500%，一月回報200%，令人非常不安。"},{"pid":"68cacdd76b38aa96469860dc1f9c4a05724d40b8","tid":2356385,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:11:31.000Z","msg":"淨係知而家講跌會比人笑"},{"pid":"6f0a040d61766747060fcb6a485f066deff56c7a","tid":2356385,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"4259ae74d70967191596010386ac73afd6e21a00","tid":2356385,"uid":368597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"已經聽到啦 返工嗰陣聽到兩個阿姨喺度講股票 但一聽就知佢哋唔撚識"},{"pid":"967cfc6cd4de725b91de4a46a296fa3319d2f2b4","tid":2356385,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"好多野都普及化啦，用部電話就搞掂。唔出奇。亦冇必要睇唔起人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf5cd1aa442993a24ec57020bac6f92413807bd","tid":2356385,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4259ae74d70967191596010386ac73afd6e21a00","tid":2356385,"uid":368597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"已經聽到啦 返工嗰陣聽到兩個阿姨喺度講股票 但一聽就知佢哋唔撚識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:14:03.000Z","msg":"想知佢哋係講咩股票？同埋係齋講定買？"},{"pid":"dd68892182d3c927fdb9d6d930d7d3ebb8569463","tid":2356385,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:16:29.000Z","msg":"多人買就自然易回調<br />\n但宜家有電話唔同玩法"},{"pid":"18a11ec4c044b5c0be52205a696870fcefc4f109","tid":2356385,"uid":368597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf5cd1aa442993a24ec57020bac6f92413807bd","tid":2356385,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4259ae74d70967191596010386ac73afd6e21a00","tid":2356385,"uid":368597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"已經聽到啦 返工嗰陣聽到兩個阿姨喺度講股票 但一聽就知佢哋唔撚識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:14:03.000Z","msg":"想知佢哋係講咩股票？同埋係齋講定買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:18:31.000Z","msg":"ATMX<br />\n我聽到嘅係一個有買叫另一個去買"},{"pid":"8d25d1ecee55613f52e246dc71ea727e5b4a78fe","tid":2356385,"uid":177572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"唔同，而家係打緊無限<span class=\"x-small\">QE</span>之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03b31e91a7ab39a30ae0cadb567a22fd5867382","tid":2356385,"uid":208280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T21:57:38.000Z","msg":"賣菜其實好好賺，分分鐘樓下街市賣菜阿姐揸住幾百萬騰訊你都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cla